							<RECORD id="0-0-0-56237" number="64289" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 17-01 Scope.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-7685" name="T28C017_17-01"/>§ 17-01 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Scope.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56238" number="64290" version="1863">
									<PARA>This chapter describes the process for making objections to municipal charges that are enforced as tax liens against properties pursuant to §§ <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2144" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2144</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2153" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2153</LINK>(q), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2091" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2091</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(f)(8), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(k), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="28-215.1.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">28-215.1.1</LINK> and <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="28-216.11" destination-id="0-0-0-0">28-216.11</LINK> of the Administrative Code and any other municipal charges that may be made tax liens subject to the process described in Article 8 of Subchapter 5 of the Housing Maintenance Code. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56239" number="64291" version="55">
									<PARA>(Amended City Record 7/21/2015, eff. 8/20/2015) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-56240" number="64292" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 17-02 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-7687" name="T28C017_17-02"/>§ 17-02 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Definitions.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56241" number="64293" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>In this chapter, the following terms have the following meanings:</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56242" number="64294" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Administrative Code&quot; means the New York City Administrative Code.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56243" number="64295" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Billing Application Detail&quot; means a record kept by the Department of Finance that contains the date of a statement of account.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56244" number="64296" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Commissioner&quot; means the Commissioner of the Department of Housing Preservation and Development or a person designated by him or her to exercise his or her powers set forth in this chapter.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56245" number="64297" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(4)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Department&quot; means the Department of Housing Preservation and Development.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56246" number="64298" version="2306">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(5)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Housing Maintenance Code&quot; means <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T27C002" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 2 of Title 27</LINK> of the Administrative Code.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56247" number="64299" version="1863">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(6)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Owner&quot; has the same meaning as described in Multiple Dwelling Law § 4(44) and Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2004" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2004</LINK>(45)(a).</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56248" number="64300" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(7)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Statement of Account&quot; means a bill for taxes, charges and assessments that the Department of Finance sends to owners of real property.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56249" number="64301" version="1863">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(8)<TAB tab-count="1"/>&quot;Tax Lien&quot; means a lien arising pursuant to the provisions of <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C003" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 3 of Title 11</LINK> of the Administrative Code as a result of the nonpayment of any charges that are made a lien subject to the provisions of such chapter including any interest and penalties.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-56250" number="64302" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 17-03 Objection Procedure.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-7689" name="T28C017_17-03"/>§ 17-03 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Objection Procedure.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56251" number="64303" version="1900">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Department may file a lien for its expenses and fees incurred pursuant to Administrative Code §§ <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2144" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2144</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2153" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2153</LINK>(q), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2091" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2091</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(f)(8), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(k), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="28-215.1.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">28-215.1.1</LINK> and <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="28-216.11" destination-id="0-0-0-0">28-216.11</LINK>. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56252" number="64304" version="1863">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Unless otherwise stated in Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2146" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2146</LINK> and these rules,</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56253" number="64305" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>an owner, or</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56254" number="64306" version="1864">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>a mortgagee or lienor, whose mortgage or lien would have priority over the Department&apos;s lien if not for the provisions of § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2144" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2144</LINK>, who receives a statement of account pursuant to Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2129" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2129</LINK> with a charge incurred pursuant to Administrative Code §§ <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2125" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2125</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2153" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2153</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2091" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2091</LINK>, <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(f)(8), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(k), <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="28-215.1.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">28-215.1.1</LINK> or <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="28-216.11" destination-id="0-0-0-0">28-216.11</LINK> may notify the Department in writing of his or her objection to such charge. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56255" number="64307" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The &quot;statement date&quot; listed on the Department of Finance&apos;s billing application detail for a statement of account shall be presumptive evidence that such statement of account was mailed within five business days of the statement date to the person or entity registered with the Department of Finance.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56256" number="64308" version="1064">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>All objections to a charge on a statement of account shall be submitted in writing or electronically. Each objection shall be addressed to the Department to the attention of the Research and Reconciliation Unit, 100 Gold Street,New York, N.Y. 10038 or to hpderp@hpd.nyc.gov. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56257" number="64309" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(e)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Each objection to a charge on a statement of account shall:</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56258" number="64310" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>specify the charge objected to and the nature of such objection, and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56259" number="64311" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>include any documentation supporting the objection. </PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56260" number="64312" version="3">
									<PARA>Any charge without specific objections from an owner shall be considered undisputed.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56261" number="64313" version="1865">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(f)<TAB tab-count="1"/>If an owner submits an objection under Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2129" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2129</LINK> and 28 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T28C047_47-02" destination-id="0-0-0-8225">47-02</LINK> to a charge imposed under § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(f)(8) on the basis that he or she has attempted and failed to gain access to the dwelling unit that is the subject of the complaint-based inspection fee for the purpose of making repairs, then the owner shall include the following documentation: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56262" number="64314" version="1163">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(i)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Copies of at least four written notices delivered to the occupant of the subject dwelling unit (two attempts at access after each complaint-based inspection) requesting access at reasonable dates and times in accordance with 28 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T28C025_25-101" destination-id="0-0-0-7827">25-101</LINK>, to make repairs. However, if the owner is requesting access to repair a class C violation, copies of such written notices will not be required unless such class C violation is for the existence of a lead-based paint hazard; and</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56263" number="64315" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(ii)<TAB tab-count="1"/>A sworn affidavit signed by the owner, that such owner or his or her representative was not able, after four attempts (two attempts at access after each complaint-based inspection), to gain access to the dwelling unit for the purpose of making repairs. Such affidavit shall include the date of each such attempt at access and shall describe the efforts made by the owner or his or her representative to obtain access to the dwelling unit, and such other information as the Department may require. When an owner requests access to repair a class C violation that is not for lead-based paint, the affidavit shall include details of the actions taken by the owner or his or her representative to notify the occupant of the subject dwelling unit, including, but not limited to, making telephone calls, sending emails, and knocking on the occupant&apos;s door at a reasonable time when he or she would be expected to be present. Such affidavit shall include the date and time of such actions. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56264" number="64316" version="1865">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(g)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Each objection to a charge on a statement of account shall be received by the Department prior to the due and payable date of such charge. Pursuant to Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2129" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2129</LINK>, if an owner does not notify the Department in writing of his or her objection to such a charge before the due and payable date as indicated on the statement of account, the owner may not contest the charge in any subsequent judicial or administrative proceeding. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56265" number="64317" version="1865">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(h)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Unless otherwise stated in subdivision (c) of Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2146" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2146</LINK>, a written objection to a charge on a statement of account may not be based upon: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56266" number="64318" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the lawfulness of the repair or other work done or, <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56267" number="64319" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the propriety and accuracy of the expense for which a lien is claimed. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56268" number="64320" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(i)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Within a reasonable time after receipt of a written objection to a charge on a statement of account, the Department will make a determination based on all the documentation received from the objecting owner as well as the records of the Department. The Department will then inform the objecting owner of such determination in writing, including the reasons for that decision. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-56269" number="64321" version="55">
									<PARA>(Amended City Record 7/21/2015, eff. 8/20/2015) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>